snippet.title: Billie Eilish - NDA (Official Music Video) REACTION!
snippet.description:
her habits has appeared once again to first vent about her life and then react to Billie Eilish's brand new song and music video for "NDA" from her upcoming album "Happier Than Ever". Hope you enjoy!

0:00 - MY LONG RAMBLE RIDDEN INTRO
5:58 - REACTION FINALLY BEGINS
